echo -e "\e[31m‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îò\e[0m"
echo ""

# -------------------------------
# 1Ô∏è‚É£ Proxy File Check
# -------------------------------
PROXY_FILE="proxy.txt"
INTERVAL=15  # har 15 sec me proxy change hoga

if [[ ! -f "$PROXY_FILE" ]]; then
    echo "‚ùå Proxy list file ($PROXY_FILE) not found!"
    exit 1
fi

echo -e "\e[1;33m[+] Hybrid Proxy Rotator Started (Interval: ${INTERVAL}s)\e[0m"

# -------------------------------
# 2Ô∏è‚É£ Loop for Proxy Rotation
# -------------------------------
while true; do
    PROXY=$(shuf -n 1 "$PROXY_FILE")  # random proxy pick
    IP=$(echo "$PROXY" | cut -d: -f1)
    PORT=$(echo "$PROXY" | cut -d: -f2)

    if [[ "$PORT" == "1080" || "$PORT" == "4153" || "$PORT" == "16379" || "$PORT" == "39593" ]]; then
        TYPE="SOCKS5"
        NEW_IP=$(curl --socks5 $PROXY -s --max-time 10 https://api64.ipify.org)
    else
        TYPE="HTTP"
        NEW_IP=$(curl -x http://$PROXY -s --max-time 10 https://api64.ipify.org)
    fi

    if [[ -n "$NEW_IP" ]]; then
        echo -e "\e[1;32müåê Using [$TYPE] Proxy: $PROXY ‚Üí IP: $NEW_IP ‚úÖ\e[0m"
    else
        echo -e "\e[1;31m‚ö†Ô∏è Proxy $PROXY ($TYPE) not working!\e[0m"
    fi

    echo "----------------------------------"
    sleep $INTERVAL
done



